title: Photos: Lady Gaga Rocks Super Bowl 51 Halftime Show
text:
Photos: Lady Gaga Rocks Super Bowl 51 Halftime Show February 6, 2017 2:59 AM (Photo by Christopher Polk/Getty Images) 
Lady Gaga ROCKED THE HOUSE last night at Super Bowl 51. 
Lady Gaga CRUSHED her Halftime performance. She started on the roof of the stadium, then jumped off (on wires of course). She did a medley of her hits, and it sounds like she did the whole thing LIVE. (Photo by Patrick Smith/Getty Images) (Photo by Christopher Polk/Getty Images) (Photo by Christopher Polk/Getty Images) (Photo by Patrick Smith/Getty Images)
